Convik
------
Digital brushless motor controller.

Project information can be found at https://github.com/greghaynes/Convik/wiki

------
Convik Demo Board

Files marked board-demo are for a breadboard version that exists for testing and which is independent of quadcopter power distribution. Not final on-board version. 

